data.description: Multi use 1.5 acre ranchette property in east Gridley with 3 bed. 2 bath ranch style home. Fireplace, great room, island kitchen, swimming pool, patio, deck and several outbuildings. Bring your animals and ranch it up! Come see this private country home that isn't secluded. Located in East Gridley, there's plenty of room to roam. Loaded with fruit, citrus and nut trees and tons of shade! Make it yours before someone else does.
